I found my components were not updating properly. I then simplified it to the version I have now, and I still cannot get the loader to display.

My impression was that calling `StateHasChanged` in my `RunTest()` function would reload things but it looks like its only ever reloading one time, when the execution of the function is complete. My loading spinner never renders and my results component never gets hidden based on the if blocks around each of them. 

